# Window Presets (`touch-window-presets`)

## When to Use
- Apply prebuilt desktop layouts in one action.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `window.presets`
- Commands: `window / preset / layout / 分屏 / 布局`

## Core Capabilities
- 窗口预设：一键应用常用桌面布局
- Supported platforms: `win32`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: None (no manual config file needed for MVP)
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-window-presets`

## Permissions
- Required: `system.shell`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `window`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
